Types of Design Patterns:
==========================

CREATIONAL [ creation of object ]

 -> Singleton
 -> Factory
 -> Abstract Factory
 -> Builder
 -> Prototype

STRUCTURAL [ compose one object in another object ]

 -> Adaptor
 -> Composite
 -> Proxyu
 -> Fly weight
 -> Facade
 -> Bridge
 -> Decorator

BEHAVIOURAL [ handle two objects ]

 -> Template Method
 -> Mediator
 -> Chain of responsibility
 -> Observer
 -> Stretegy
 -> Command
 -> State
 -> Visitor
 -> Interface
 -> Interpertor
 -> memento



